    "Using AI and MD simulations to explore polymer systems presents specific challenges, as it is difficult to apply a single workflow for highthroughput simulation and evaluation.",
    "However, we believe this study serves as a first step toward more accurate methods, such as accelerated simulations and machine-learned force fields, which will improve the accuracy of computed ion transport properties in the future.",
    "Our approach aims to narrow the search space and identify promising candidates that can be explored experimentally for final validation, laying the groundwork for more targeted and efficient polymer discovery.",
    "Finally, this work only touches on the minimal level of complexity of polymer electrolyte materials, focusing on the chemistry of a single repeating unit.",
    "However, the true complexity of polymers lies beyond."
